{"tid":448611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出現了！下星期溫度跌至19度！！","createTime":"2017-10-26T11:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T05:53:14.000Z","uid":1886,"like":83,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"ab64d019ba52f0aa4c0568bda43b2abffeffca57","tid":448611,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"天文台表示，下周初將有一股東北季候風補充為本港帶來稍涼的天氣。天文台預測，下周二（31日）氣溫跌穿攝氏20度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，低見19度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最高氣溫也只有約攝氏24度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當晚準備外出慶祝萬聖節的市民記得加衣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171026/s00001/1508992317625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171026%2Fs00001%2F1508992317625&d=zlQSdwqrDzpYYHyGoHHUOsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=681f7c0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171026%2Fs00001%2F1508992317625&h=d0a4a1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171026/s00001/1508992317625</a>"},{"pid":"4e27eb1001dba743059bf8c7cd01f19ff9c6346e","tid":448611,"uid":29080,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"又要射波了"},{"pid":"16301b67ee10a327fe215b0bfe15b3a63aad5444","tid":448611,"uid":108947,"like":86,"dislike":4,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"上個星期已經係咁講啦, 我夜晚訓教仲要開風扇, 仲要狼來了多幾多次先係真呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6c5d48e7d5778c8a765d669a346b0cb62c41b2","tid":448611,"uid":132038,"like":31,"dislike":65,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"